# Day 50 – Defend Your Experience

##  Overview
For Day 50 of the **#60DayClaudeChallenge**, I built an interactive **Defend Your Experience** dashboard using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

The application simulates realistic interview scenarios by challenging users to confidently defend the claims made in their resume, portfolio, projects, or professional experience. It provides an adaptive interview workflow, tracks progress, and generates a structured Defense Report to help users identify strengths and areas for improvement.

---

##  Features

- Interactive interview dashboard
- Resume and portfolio upload interface
- Adaptive follow-up questioning
- Experience defense workflow
- Confidence progress tracking
- AI-inspired Defense Report
- Session history
- Local Storage support
- Export functionality
- Responsive dark-mode UI

---

